data.name: Index Ticker

description:
The BitMEX Price Index developed by Kaiko provides the reference price on which all BitMEX Bitcoin Products are priced. It is freely available and easily replicable.
Weights of the exchanges : The weights are calculated every last Friday of the month at 12:01 UTC . The previous 30 days of trade volume data are used in this calculation. BTC-USD trades from OKCoin, Bitfinex and Bitstamp are included. No exchange may have a weight over 50%
Price update : The price is updated every 5 seconds. The BitMEX index is available 24/7.
